      "Here are the steps I have been using to test some things in VMs:\r\n1. `sudo curl -O 'http://people.centos.org/tru/devtools-2/' /etc/yum.repos.d/`\r\n2. `sudo sh -c 'echo \"enabled=1\" >> /etc/yum.repos.d/devtools-2.repo'`\r\n3. `sudo yum install openssl-devel devtoolset-2-gcc devtoolset-2-binutils devtoolset-2-gcc-c++`\r\n4. `scl enable devtoolset-2 bash` The new compiler is not the default, so this goes into an environment where it is.\r\n\r\nThen the usual:\r\n1. `git clone https://github.com/rethinkdb/rethinkdb.git`\r\n2. `cd rethinkdb`\r\n3. `./configure --allow-fetch`\r\n4. `make`"
